# 🐦 BirdVision

## 🚀 AI Bird Detection System

This is a bird detection system I built using AI.  
It can detect and identify birds from **images, videos, and live camera feed**.

---

### ⚡ Core Idea

- YOLO → finds the bird  
- ResNet → tells what bird it is  

Also supports:
- English labels  
- Sinhala labels  

---

## 🔥 What it can do

- Detect birds from images  
- Process videos frame-by-frame  
- Run real-time detection using webcam  
- Show bird name + confidence  
- Show Sinhala translation  

---

## 🧠 How it works (simple)

1. YOLOv8 detects the bird  
2. Crop detected region  
3. ResNet50 classifies it  
4. Draw result on screen  

